# Kendo Price Dashboard

A price tracking dashboard built with **KendoReact** and modern JavaScript tools.  
This project visualizes product prices from e-commerce websites in real time and displays them in an interactive dashboard.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 📊 Interactive price charts and tables with **KendoReact**
- 🌐 Real-time data fetching from e-commerce sites
- 🔄 Automatic price updates
- 📁 Organized codebase with reusable components
- ⚡ Built with **React + Vite** for fast development

---

