## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React, Vite, KendoReact
- **Backend (optional)**: Node.js, Express
- **Data Fetching**: Axios, Bright Data proxy
- **Version Control**: Git & GitHub

---

## 📂 Project Structure
kendo-price-dashboard/ |- public/ #Static files  |- src/ #React components & logic| |- components/ #Reusable UI components| |- pages/ #Dashboard pages| |- App.jsx # Main app entry |- package.json # Dependencies & scripts |- vite.config.js # Vite configuration |- README.md # Project documentation 

Installation & Setup:
Clone the repository:
..... bash
git clone 
https://github.com/oboh12/kendo-price-dashboard.git
   cd  kendo-price-dashboard

Install dependencies:
npm install 

Start development server:
npm start 

Build for production:
npm run build 

